headline: IEM Launches New Experiential Retail Innovation Platform at Simon with High-Growth Brands
summary: IEM, a venture-backed retail innovation company, and Simon®, a real estate investment trust engaged in the ownership of premier shopping, dining, entertainment and mixed-use destinations, today announced the rollout of new platform built to help high-growth brands scale into brick-and-mortar quickly and flexibly.
